<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Ruff</span></h1>
<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
<div id="contentSub">  (Redirected from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Philomachus_pugnax&amp;redirect=no" title="Philomachus pugnax">Philomachus pugnax</a>)</div>
<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
Jump to: <a href="Philomachus_pugnax#mw-navigation">navigation</a>, <a href="Philomachus_pugnax#p-search">search</a>
</div>
